OL,3,CPlaque unveiled for man who built M1,
OL,4,CBritish Library and Coventry Cathedral
OL,6,FA plaque has been unveiled to remember
OL,7,Fthe man who built the M1, British
OL,8,FLibrary and Coventry Cathedral at his
OL,9,Fformer home in Carlisle.
OL,11,FSir John Laing founded an
OL,12,Finternational construction business
OL,13,Fand oversaw the building of the most
OL,14,Ficonic buildings in the country.
OL,16,FHe was also responsible more locally
OL,17,Ffor building the Sands Centre, Lanes
OL,18,FShopping Centre and thousands of homes
OL,19,Facross Carlisle.
