OL,3,CPlaque unveiled for man who built M1,
OL,4,CBritish Library and Coventry Cathedral
OL,6,FA national blue plaque has now been
OL,7,Finstalled on his former home on
OL,8,FNewcastle Street in the city to
OL,9,Fcelebrate his life and achievements.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Border, Mike Little
OL,12,Fthe Chair of the Carlisle Civic Trust,
OL,13,Fsaid: "There's hardly anyone in
OL,14,FCarlisle that doesn't know someone
OL,15,Fsomewhere associated with John Laing.
OL,16,FHe built his business up here.
OL,18,F"I mean, there are literally thousands
OL,19,Fof homes in Carlisle built by John
OL,20,FLaing, all employing local Carlisle
OL,21,Fpeople.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
