OL,3,CPlaque unveiled for man who built M1,
OL,4,CBritish Library and Coventry Cathedral
OL,6,F"He was a committed Christian and
OL,7,Fphilanthropist. He was a real people
OL,8,Fperson. He believed in caring for
OL,9,Fpeople, looking after his workforce.
OL,11,F"In the 50s and 60s it was unusual to
OL,12,Fhave company pension schemes, payment
OL,13,Fwhile you're on holiday. These were
OL,14,Fquite novel things and John introduced
OL,15,Fthis, he was among the first.
OL,17,F"And here in Carlisle so we are quite
OL,18,Fproud of him."
