OL,6,FThe great-granddaughter and great-
OL,7,Fgrandson of Sir John Laing were in
OL,8,Fattendance at Newcastle Street to see
OL,9,Fthe plaque.
OL,11,FAlexandra Gregory said: "When we were
OL,12,Fyoung we didn't really see everything
OL,13,Fthat he did. But the more we talk to
OL,14,Fpeople and we're involved in the
OL,15,Fretirement clubs as well as around the
OL,16,Fcountry.
OL,18,F"So we hear from the retired employees
OL,19,Fa lot about what he did and it is
OL,20,Fwonderful."
